snippet.textDisplay:
I can see this song getting popular these days through reels and clips.
Now many of the 'new music lovers' will hear the name of farhaan saeed for the 1st time and think this to be his best song ever. I feel fortunate enough that I know farhaan since the days of jal. Aadat, woh lamhe, Sajni all these superhits of early 20s were sung by this man. That era is gone now, the man has grown old now but the music and those memories are still fresh and clear.❣️
